[[Image:The Lord of the Rings Film Calendar 1980.jpg|thumb]]

'''The Lord of the Rings Film Calendar 1980''' was produced by [[Saul Zaentz Production Co.]] and printed by Chorley and Pickersgrill Ltd., Leeds. Illustrations were from the 1978 film ''[[The Lord of the Rings (1978 film)|The Lord of the Rings]]''.

* ISBN 0-04-5290067
* Dimensions: 12 3/8 x 12.5 inches
* Wire bound
* Heavy wire hanging loop
* Plastic zip-lock bag imprinted in green with title
